.TH "ata_eh_set_pending" 9 "ata_eh_set_pending" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ata_eh_set_pending \- set ATA_PFLAG_EH_PENDING and activate fast drain
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" ata_eh_set_pending
.BI "(struct ata_port *ap "  ","
.BI "int fastdrain "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ap" 12
target ATA port
.IP "fastdrain" 12
activate fast drain

Set ATA_PFLAG_EH_PENDING and activate fast drain if \fIfastdrain\fP
is non-zero and EH wasn't pending before.  Fast drain ensures
that EH kicks in in timely manner.

LOCKING:
spin_lock_irqsave(host lock)
